{"tid":1652381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(人手置頂)高級五毛團體入侵警告！！！！！！！疑似白卡佬出沒！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-10-13T16:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T03:23:35.000Z","uid":79793,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4d47f80c3e85f3950315eaf946b5f825244fa5f","tid":1652381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:01:41.000Z","msg":"我已經開過好多個Post,講最近好多迷信post出黎<br />\n希望大家保持觀望態度，討論還討論，唔好沉迷呢d迷信野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">迷信文章出現時間點</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">831&gt;即刻有極多陰陽眼話見到野<br />\n中大女學生&gt;預言,作法</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">如果大家仲相信呢個所謂的gay大師請睇下呢個post,一定笑撚到你仆街</span></span></strong><br />\n如果講大話我裸跑！！我真係識法術唔信嘅話入嚟睇我預言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ajRHjjU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ajRHjjU</a><br />\n呢位巴打尻吹撚佢地都有人信<br />\n<br />\n佢地開POST極多疑點<br />\n<strong>手足一出去或者訓左就會出現垃圾靈異POST</strong><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648701</a><br />\n<br />\n佢地係高級五毛分化撚,迷信post有極大量P牌(30萬以上)互吹水,只要你反駁佢地<br />\n佢就會有組織性話你係狗,甚至係國安<br />\n我就係其中一個比人話國安嘅人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲主張睇唔過眼就叫手足block人</span></span></strong><br />\n佢地會話起底冇用,國安HACK左AC,因為佢地駁唔到點解我堂堂一個國安幾個星期前開POST叫大家玩魔獸世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢位GAY大師應該係想轉移視線推走行動POST，仲有巴打話佢係之前波台白卡佬</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好同我講法術救國，咁撚勁一早就有人落降頭，收皮啦迷信狗</span></strong></em><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/FUAKZImGkRax2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FFUAKZImGkRax2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=8a73c640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n持續追擊迷信狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n()係開POST數量<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">9個30萬P牌號長期推POST</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">IamGay<br />\n#324135 (3)P<br />\n無地卡羅<br />\n#290585  (0)P<br />\n給我撐10秒<br />\n#293852 (2)P<br />\n吉茵珂絲<br />\n#259319 (9)P<br />\n西瓜的夏天<br />\n#298055 (0)P<br />\n支那坦克人<br />\n#300815 (0)P<br />\n市民（暴徒喬裝）<br />\n#263412 (0)P<br />\n女農夫<br />\n#288678 (3)P<br />\n你估我想呀<br />\n#310885 (0)P 上個名叫非洲灰姑娘1 小時前<br />\n奇趣小丑<br />\n#331696(0)P<br />\n饅頭蛙<br />\n#261971(1)P<br />\n殘忍的雙丸<br />\n#301233(0)P<br />\n南瓜牛肉球<br />\n#79530(0)非P<br />\n十月的天空很乾淨<br />\n#314462(7)P<br />\n撚貓達人<br />\n#270943(2)P<br />\n空白的紙條<br />\n#314178(4)P<br />\n懦夫(女)<br />\n#305357(0)P<br />\n奇趣小丑<br />\n#331696(0)P</span>"},{"pid":"42ba65f92ff36d0a26c237e25b329245aebaf2de","tid":1652381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:02:50.000Z","msg":"持續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b5cf566a7942fac311838e11da9d0daa3731501","tid":1652381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"持續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c516956671e87525f6a8f6524beef686c25c8492","tid":1652381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"持續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d6241e39a1f96a752d8523e8830b6f710131cb","tid":1652381,"uid":79793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"持續追擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6186fff6ffa38f7134ffcd7938e60e57b3cc7ec2","tid":1652381,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-1